features: NATURAL BABY WIPES: Our products are independently certified natural and organic by Ecocert COSMOS and OK Biobased TÜV. These hypoallergenic baby wipes are made from 100% natural, ultrathin fibers that are soft, compostable, and plant based.
FOR SENSITIVE SKIN: We make our baby wipes unscented and hypoallergenic to help eliminate irritants and allergens, making them the perfect newborn baby wipes.
COMPOSTABLE AND ECO-FRIENDLY: Because of their plant-based fibers and pure water content, these eco-friendly baby wipes decompose in just 12 weeks. And you can compost them at home!

CLEAN AND GREEN: Whether your baby has sensitive skin or not, using plant-based baby diaper wipes made from certified organic plant materials and pure water without synthetics or chemicals is simply better for their skin.

GOOD FOR BABY, GOOD FOR NATURE: Eco by Naty was first started in Sweden nearly 27 years ago. Today, we continue with our goal to create products that are not only safe for our bodies, but that are also good for the environment. Our High-Tech Eco Products are backed by independent sustainability certifications, we offer the greenest products, all made from nature!
body.description: Give your baby’s bum the VIP treatment with our extra soft and thick wipes enriched with soothing chamomile. Naty wipes are made from natural ingredients, and are chlorine, plastic and perfume free. Our wipes have been independently certified to be 100% compostable, which means that no toxic lotions have been added that might make your tomatoes glow purple. And because they’re dermatologically tested, you can chill out about nappy rash and nasty allergic reactions too.

reviews.reviewText: These are so durable and amazing. They are just like name brand wipes, but better for the earth. I'm 100% sold and will continue to buy these as long as they are available.I use them to wash my face before bed and take them along on long car rides and overnight trips.They are a great size, stay wet after being opened, and don't leave fuzz behind. What more could I ask for?

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Sensitive Skin Rash
reviews.reviewText: I purchased the Eco by Naty Unscented Baby Wipes with high hopes for an eco-friendly and non-toxic makeup wipe alternative. Unfortunately, my experience fell short of expectations.While the compostable and plant-based aspect is commendable, the wipes proved harsh on my skin, particularly around the eyes. I encountered a rash after using them to remove mascara. The texture of the wipes is not soft, and they lack the durability needed for effective makeup removal.Considering the sensitivity these wipes caused on my skin, I would be cautious about using them on a baby or child, especially on delicate areas. The intention to choose an eco-friendly option is appreciated, but the product's effectiveness and potential skin irritation need improvement.Currently using them for cleaning and they have worked better for that.

Verwende ich in unserem Garten-Kompostklo ! Tolles Produkt ! Wir waren damals schon von den Windeln begeistert.

After being a big fan of the Neutral wipes for years (both kids never had diaper rash, ever!), I wanted to try something that was more eco friendly but still of the same quality as Neutral and it did not disappoint! The only two things I can think of are that they lose a bit of tissue (tiny fluff balls) that collect in the usual places and the scent is a bit comparable perfumeless sunscreen. All in all a very good alternative to the less environment friendly brands.
